{
  "stem": "24268.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She went to the cousins, which they-- they had the connection.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they told, don't worry, you'll be out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he went to the head of the shop, and he told them to let us out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But the Jewish community said, well, they cannot do it, because they have to wait for the authorities from the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, we got in, and I was sent to the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also, this is the place, [INAUDIBLE] where all, whoever they grabbed, was concentrated in this place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was-- so I was in it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after they were-- they taking me to this place, they say, we should have not taken you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You weren't on the list.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We say, well, what's the difference?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They are [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on this [INAUDIBLE], they segregated, every time they make an appel and the SS came, and they took out certain group, or whoever they want to.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Depends what camp they want to send.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wherever the need was, to different camps, to ladies' camps, or to death camps, or to men's camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That time, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when they took me, my mom remained with my sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was in this [GERMAN], they called, so all I saw for the last before I-- that was the last time I saw my mom and my sister and my youngest cousin, when I went to the window, and my mom tried to motion to me I shouldn't cry.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said she'll come to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the last time I saw my family, my mom, my sister, and my cousin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after that, I asked the-- the man who was in charge of this, before they send us to camp, he was in charge of all the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
